@lap v0.3
# Machine-readable API spec. Each @endpoint block is one API call.
@api Events API
@base https://events.1password.com
@version 1.2.0
@auth Bearer bearer
@endpoints 5
@toc api(5)

@endpoint GET /api/auth/introspect
